  ANIMALS OF THE WORLD
============================================================

Name:         Blue Whale
Scientific:   Balaenoptera musculus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore (krill)
Lifespan:     80 years
Weight:       150000 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Largest animal ever known; heart is size of a small car

Name:         African Elephant
Scientific:   Loxodonta africana
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     70 years
Weight:       6000 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Largest land animal; strongest sense of smell; mourns the dead

Name:         Axolotl
Scientific:   Ambystoma mexicanum
Class:        Amphibia
Habitat:      Lakes
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       0.3 kg
Status:       Critically Endangered
Fact:         Can regenerate entire limbs, spine, heart, and brain tissue

